title: Week 6 NFL Recap: The Giants top Ravens at home, the Eagles dominate, and the Jets roll over the Packers (Football 10/17)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson, and John Breech recap an interesting Week 6 in the NFL. The Giants win again, the Eagles dominate while staying undefeated, and the Jets roll over the Packers in Lambeau.

Eagles-Cowboys (2:00)
Bills-Chiefs (16:00)
Jets-Packers (28:20)
Giants-Ravens (37:00)
Bengals-Saints (44:20)
Steelers-Bucs (49:10)
Falcons-49ers (59:00)
Patriots-Browns (1:04:40)
Vikings-Dolphins (1:13:00)
Rams-Panthers (1:17:00)
Seahawks-Cardinals (1:21:57)
Colts-Jaguars (1:28:33)
